nT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Ph%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A2m-ca/poem-cC9BgQ8wCRkxD4aCpfpwXw">Phật tâm ca - 佛心歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Huy/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Anh-t%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-ZXtaaHRcnb0xPBT8aFVJCQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Anh tài tử” - 奉和御製英才子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Huy/author-u7o28HI1zNHlA8xR5PeQ2A">Đàm Thận Huy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-tr%E1%BA%ADn-vong/poem-JnHWJb5Kd6-M07NFz1l5Zw">Tế trận vong - 祭陣亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-h%E1%BB%AFu-v%C3%A3n-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-bU4FsHTcPEKg-qUea-hNMA">Tịnh hữu vãn thi kỳ 3 - 并有輓詩其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
